cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP_INSTREAMS to 0 creates a logical contradiction as it disables input streams, preventing any data reception on the SCTP connection between CU and DU, leading to connection failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_dl to identical values [285, 285] causes timing misalignment in the downlink compression parameters, potentially leading to synchronization issues and degraded performance in the front-haul interface.
